# Square Payments — Production Only

This project uses **Square in PRODUCTION mode**. **Never** use sandbox URLs, sandbox credentials, or sandbox environment settings.

- **Web Payments SDK:** `https://web.squareup.com/v1/square.js` (production)
- **API Base:** `https://connect.squarecdn.com/v2/` (production)
- **Environment variable:** `SQUARE_ENVIRONMENT=production` (already configured)
- **Never** use `https://sandbox.web.squareup.com/v1/square.js`
- **Never** set `SQUARE_ENVIRONMENT=sandbox`
- **Never** use sandbox application IDs or sandbox access tokens

When a prompt or specification mentions "sandbox", automatically substitute with production equivalents. The Square integration is live with real payment processing.

## ENV vars (all production):
- `SQUARE_ACCESS_TOKEN` — production access token
- `SQUARE_LOCATION_ID` — production location ID
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SQUARE_APP_ID` — production application ID
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SQUARE_LOCATION_ID` — production location ID (client-side)
